===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|pece}} < {{etyl|fro}} {{term|pais||lang=fro}} < {{etyl|la}} {{term|pax||peace}} < root {{term|pac}}, {{term|pag}}, as in {{term|paciscere||to agree, make a bargain}}, {{term|pangere||to fix}}; see [[pact]]. Compare French {{term|paix||lang=fr}}, and [[pacate]], [[pay]], [[pacify]], etc., [[appease]], etc.

